# External Projects - Read Only

The following directories are **external Git repositories** cloned for reference and study. They must NEVER be modified:

- `paperclip/` — AI employee platform (https://github.com/yinshunyao/paperclip.git)
- `agency-agents-zh/` — AI agent expert team (https://github.com/yinshunyao/agency-agents-zh.git)

## Rules

1. **Never create, edit, or delete** any file under `paperclip/` or `agency-agents-zh/`
2. **Read and search only** — use these projects as references to understand patterns, APIs, and architecture
3. When the user asks about these projects, **read and explain** the code but do not propose changes to it
4. If functionality from these projects needs to be reused, **copy or adapt** the relevant code into the project's own directories (e.g. `codiiy/`, `refrence/`, or new directories at the workspace root)
